    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扩展内容包：《大唐传说系列》包含两套服装</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >服装1：<br>【大唐明光甲：传奇甲胄】</h2> &quot;拨开时间的尘封卷帙，轻启历史的悠长篇章&quot;。大唐明光甲这不仅是一件防御装备，更是一部流动的历史画卷，一幅精美的艺术杰作，它将唐代的军事文化、工艺美学与哲学思想融为一体。<br>大唐明光甲的设计灵感源自唐代都力求还原唐代甲胄的神韵与风采。在欣赏其艺术之美的同时，也能深刻体会到大唐盛世的磅礴气势与文化底蕴。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173800/extras/abd63c8a0223205a5e7498f7da8d69f5.poster.avif?t=1726025818\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173800/extras/abd63c8a0223205a5e7498f7da8d69f5.webm?t=1726025818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173800/extras/abd63c8a0223205a5e7498f7da8d69f5.mp4?t=1726025818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >服装2：<br>【红丝唐装：传说中的东方秘宝】</h2>“晨曦微露，霞光万道，一抹传奇的红，如同初升的太阳般炽烈而深邃”。<br>红丝唐装，不仅仅是一件衣裳，它是中国千年服饰文化的一抹亮色，承载着深厚的历史底蕴与东方美学的精粹。 它的设计灵感，源自中国悠久的丝绸文化和唐装传统。在历史的长河中不断演变，感受那份来自历史的温暖与骄傲，让这份文化之美，流传千古，永续不息。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173800/extras/f07587b9051f00a45fcffb24cc2672b8.poster.avif?t=1726025818\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173800/extras/f07587b9051f00a45fcffb24cc2672b8.webm?t=1726025818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173800/extras/f07587b9051f00a45fcffb24cc2672b8.mp4?t=1726025818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
